headline.print_headline: Thousands March in Thai Capital Against Government
headline.main: Thousands March in Thai Capital Against Government

lead_paragraph: Tens of thousands of anti-government protesters marched through the streets of Thailand's capital Saturday, reviving their whistle-blowing, traffic-blocking campaign to try to force the resignation of the country's prime minister.
